race.description: Sportsbet Supporters Of Having A Crack
race.comment: COSMIC REWARD (6) last start finished 4th over 425m at this track beaten 7 lengths (24.47) behind Big Yeti in a Grade 5 on October 24. Rates a leading player and sure to be in this for a long way. KRAKEN CHIEF (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (28.92) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Can measure up this time. I'M HONEY (4) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (34.90) at Sandown. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to give a good account. WHISKY BALLERINA (1) can measure up with the right run.
